 <ThingDef ParentName="BuildingBase">
    <defName>StWoDe_Sconce</defName>
    <label>sconce</label>
    <description>A very basic type of fortification made from earthwork. Due to their soft and grainy nature, sconces take a lot less damage from arrows or gunshots while being also more difficult to climb over. Sconces will block certain kinds of animals the same way that fences do.</description>
    <thingClass>Building</thingClass>
    <category>Building</category>
    <graphicData>
